# Datasets — large and contain identifiable video, so never committed.
# The placeholder README in each folder is kept.
DataOriginal/*
!DataOriginal/README.md
MasterData/*
!MasterData/README.md

# Recorded / benchmark video clips are provided locally, never committed.
# (benchmark_videos/ keeps its READMEs and helper scripts; only the .mp4 are ignored.)
*.mp4

# Generated experiment outputs (regenerated by the scripts)
**/outputs/
**/results/
**/figures/
*.log

# Model weights and exports.
# YOLO weights auto-download; TensorRT engines are device-specific;
# the MediaPipe pose model (.task) is a one-time download too.
# The small trained demo GRU is kept so the demo runs out of the box.
*.pt
*.onnx
*.engine
*.task
*.cache
!demo_open_house/weights/gru_core3head.pt

# Python
.venv/
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# macOS
.DS_Store
